As per comment 38 on bug 1296677, tested kernel 4.3.4-300 and the trackpad on my Acer ES1-131-CSJJ is now working again.

As per comment 39 I observe the same behaviour in that: 

kernel-4.3.3-300 trackpad works;
kernel-4.3.3-301 trackpad broken;
kernel-4.3.3-303 trackpad broken;
kernel-4.3.4-300 trackpad works.

